Installation

[Windows]
01.Uninstall previous versions.
02.Install the software.
03.Run our keygen.
04.Select a product.
05.Push "Register This Computer (Windows)".
06.Enjoy!

[MacOSX]
01.Uninstall previous versions.
02.Install the software.
03.Make your computer offline.
04.Run Authorization Manager.
05.Start offline authorization.
06.Save authorization file.
07.Open that *.html file and find your 32 digits DigitalID.
 
08.Run our keygen on Windows.
09.Select a product.
10.Input DigitalID to the keygen.
11.Push "Generate For Other Computers" and save the authorization file.
12.Open the generated file with Authorization Manager.
13.Enjoy!
